            "title": "A股午後升幅擴大    晶片股揚升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後升幅擴大，兩市合計成交13486.65億元(人民幣‧下同)，午後突破上午高位，晶片股大升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指全日升14點或0.45%，報3238點，今早開跌4點或0.12%，報3219點，約11:00am低見3211，跌0.37%或12點，為全日低位，午後升破上午高位，最高見3249，升26點或0.81%，全日成交5807.91億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指全日報9834，升79點或0.82%，今早開報9681，跌73點或0.75%，最低見9679點，跌75點或0.77%，午後高見9909，升155點或1.59%，為全日高位。全日成交7678.74億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日報3750點，收升15點或0.41%，今早開報3730，跌5點或0.13%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日報1926點，升25點或1.36%，今早開報1885，跌15點或0.79%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">半導體股領漲，華虹公司A股(滬:688347)現漲停，報52.33元，升19.75% ; 晶華微(688130.SH)升20.01%，報29.87元、美芯晟(688458.SH)升20%，報40.8元、富滿微(300671.SZ)升20%，報31.14元。</p>\n</div>",
